{"tid":518792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"由今日先開始勁憎黑警","createTime":"2018-01-03T16:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T17:50:23.000Z","uid":161030,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"48b7f43bb8ce21185f781ab02b99f1912b66e3c8","tid":518792,"uid":161030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:49:50.000Z","msg":"本身已經覺得黑警勁撚仆街<br />\n不過都未有切身經歷，所以冇乜深刻感覺<br />\n今日上警察宿命幫人補習<br />\n跟人入大閘，之後比人喝停左<br />\n「喂死𡃁仔去邊架你」<br />\n我另轉身見到個男人，應該係休班警<br />\n我話我幫人補習<br />\n佢就話登記啦死𡃁仔，當呢道自己屋企呀<br />\n講完就入左lift<br />\n嗰下就成個大堂都冇看更嘅，前幾次看更姐姐都笑住開門比我<br />\n我嗰下真係好撚嬲，估唔到黑警真係連基本尊重都唔識<br />\n唔好話佢地打份工<br />\n佢地連休左班都一樣咁撚乞人憎<br />\n我補完呢堂決定以後都唔補呢個學生<br />\n幫班黑警嘅弱智仔女溫書黎賺錢，我過唔到自己嗰關"},{"pid":"55e8e1d1ca5e9a870549694bb63c5677fda92704","tid":518792,"uid":7699,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"錢照收跟住點教就自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201489641b34022f1a8eb08f670e21b9d7195482","tid":518792,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e8e1d1ca5e9a870549694bb63c5677fda92704","tid":518792,"uid":7699,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"錢照收跟住點教就自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1246de737a9122fe9185bf9488cc10b9f9a73e00","tid":518792,"uid":90422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"黑警全家族生cancer變植物人一世死唔撚到！！！！"},{"pid":"1f2d354588c7b7b2788e92e3fa8f14fba34f8926","tid":518792,"uid":161030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"55e8e1d1ca5e9a870549694bb63c5677fda92704","tid":518792,"uid":76